body.p:
In some cases, when your document contains lots of tracked changes, you may need to hide
      the footnotes associated to the insertions, deletions, attribute changes. In the next example
      we hide the deletions, insertions, but we leave the comments visible. In your customization css, add this
      snippet:oxy-attributes,
oxy-delete,
oxy-insert{
  float:none;
  display:none;
}
